This is the safeguard within the NVO project.

==Features==
The safeguard can serve as an SDK for apps. It includes the following features:

===Root Detection===
Function: Java_edu_nvo_lib_jni_chkroot( JNIEnv *, jobject);

===Anti-Ptrace===
Function: Java_edu_nvo_lib_jni_traceme( JNIEnv *, jobject);

===Emulator Detection===
Function: Java_edu_nvo_lib_jni_chkemulator( JNIEnv *, jobject);

===Socket Connection===
Function:  Java_edu_nvo_lib_jni_socketconnect(JNIEnv *, jobject, jstring, jint);

===NVO-SHA1 Socket Connection===
Java_edu_nvo_lib_jni_secrequest(JNIEnv *, jobject, jstring, jint);

==Launch the Project==
The project can be compiled with OBOT obfuscation tool: ./build.sh 1

,or standard c++ compiler: ./build.sh
